      <!-- ── Docker Containerization ── -->
      <section class="article-section">
        <h2>Docker Containerization</h2>
        <p>Containerizing your agent ensures it runs the same way everywhere — your laptop, a CI server, or production cloud infrastructure.</p>

        <div class="code-block">
          <div class="code-header">
            <span class="code-lang">dockerfile</span>
            <span class="code-file">Dockerfile</span>
